## Title
Lemon Curd

## Recommendation Summary

### Intent Assessment
Homemade lemon curd recipe placeholder. Versatile sauce/spread/dessert component. Stub with no ingredients or instructions.

### Categorization Changes
- **PARA**: "resources" → "07-resources" (Correct as reference recipe material.)
- **GRAPH**: "links to Recipes - Sauces & Dips, Food & Nutrition List" → "Add links to Gluten Free Lemon Crinkle Cookies (lemon curd filling), Japanese Pancakes (topping), Recipes - Desserts (dessert component)" (Lemon curd bridges sauces and desserts — it fills cookies, tops pancakes, and pairs with many desserts.)

